info.description:
NYALA's tokenization API allows you to issue tokens on Polygon & Stellar. It allows you to create and manage tokens - including tokenized securities that have an ISIN - and to manage customer data. Interactions such as creating a new customer entity, request a wallet opening, creating a token and distributing a token to a customer are covered in this document.

&nbsp;

During the onboarding process, an institution entity will be created for you.
